    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduo a libvdpau-va-gl</title>

      <para>
        The <application>libvdpau-va-gl</application> package contains a library
which implements the VDPAU library.  Libvdpau_va_gl uses OpenGL under the
hood to accelerate drawing and scaling and the VA-API (if available) to
accelerate video decoding. For now VA-API is available on some Intel chips,
and on some AMD video adapters with the help of the libvdpau driver.
      </para>

      &lfs113_checked;

